---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const src = 'https://renalcarematters.com/guides/travel-dialysis-ckd.html';
---
<BaseLayout title="Travelling on dialysis" description="Travel is possible on dialysis with careful planning — booking a center ahead, clearance from your nephrologist, and the documents to bring.">
  <article class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:720px">
      <a href="/kidney-health" style="font-weight:700;text-decoration:none">← Kidney Health Hub</a>
      <h1 style="margin-top:14px">Travelling on dialysis</h1>
      <p class="lead">Kidney disease doesn't have to stop you from travelling — it just takes planning.</p>
      <p class="muted" style="font-size:.9rem">Adapted with permission from <a href={src}>renalcarematters.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>Plan earlier than usual</h2>
      <p>Most dialysis patients can travel, but it needs more lead time than for other travellers. Your
      nephrologist should clear you first, based on how stable you are right now.</p>

      <div class="notice"><strong>Book your dialysis first — before flights or hotels.</strong> Not every
      center accepts visiting patients, and slots are limited. Confirm a dialysis slot at your destination
      before you book anything else.</div>

      <h2>Who should hold off (without special clearance)</h2>
      <p>Travel needs extra caution — and explicit clearance — if you've had a recent hospitalization,
      uncontrolled blood pressure, an active infection, severe anemia or fluid overload, or a recent heart
      problem. When in doubt, ask us.</p>

      <h2>What to bring</h2>
      <ul style="line-height:1.9">
        <li>A medical summary letter from your nephrologist (in English, and the local language if possible).</li>
        <li>Your current medicine list with <strong>generic</strong> names and doses.</li>
        <li>Your dialysis prescription and recent labs.</li>
        <li>Enough of your medicines for the whole trip, plus a few extra days.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:20px"><a href="/new-patients#request" class="btn btn--primary">Ask us before you travel</a></p>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-top:22px;font-size:.9rem">Adapted with permission from
        <a href={src}>renalcarematters.com</a>. Medically reviewed by a nephrologist. Educational only;
        not a substitute for consultation.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
